<h1 style="margin:0 0 16px;font-family:Georgia,serif;font-size:24px;color:#8D153A;">Reset your password</h1>
<p style="margin:0 0 16px;line-height:1.6;">Hi {{name}},</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 24px;line-height:1.6;">We received a request to reset your {{appName}} password. This link expires in {{ttlMins}} minutes and can be used once.</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 28px;">
  <a href="{{{resetUrl}}}" style="display:inline-block;background:#EF971A;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;padding:14px 28px;font-weight:600;">Reset password</a>
</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 8px;line-height:1.6;font-size:13px;color:#666;">If the button does not work, copy this link into your browser:</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 24px;word-break:break-all;font-size:13px;"><a href="{{{resetUrl}}}" style="color:#8D153A;">{{{resetUrl}}}</a></p>
<p style="margin:0;line-height:1.6;font-size:13px;color:#666;">Did not request this? You can safely ignore this email — your password will not change.</p>
